    • AnimatedTab

      public AnimatedTab(String title, K key)
      Parameters:
      title - title of this tab
      key - when you add this to AnimatedTabPane, this will be the key of this in the keymap of the tabpane

      Of course,I dont know why I do that,maybe...it makes "managing the tabs" became easier?

      I suggest you to use a random UUID String as a key if you needn't
